      <title>美国通胀报告显示美联储的战斗现已接近完成</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/inflation-report-to-show-fed-s-battle-is-now-all-but-complete</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近几个月来，美国通胀前景已经稳步改善，但上周，就在美联储为期两天的政策会议中间，大坝终于决堤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/inflation-report-to-show-fed-s-battle-is-now-all-but-complete</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
